            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">21. A 22-year-old man presents 1 day after having been a restrained passenger in a moderate-speed motor vehicle accident (MVA). He states that his scrotum became discolored blue after the accident. He denies any trauma to the scrotum. On examination, the scrotum is bluish but the discoloration is gravity dependent. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis?</p>"
